title: Important Update: CSEET January 2026 Session Registration Deadline Passes
content:
# Important Update: CSEET January 2026 Session Registration Deadline Passes

Ek important update hai Company Secretary aspirants ke liye. The Institute of Company Secretaries of India (ICSI) ne Company Secretary Executive Entrance Test (CSEET) January 2026 session ke registration ke liye last date announce ki thi.

*   **Key Reminder:** The last date for registration for the CSEET January 2026 session was December 15, 2025.
*   This crucial information was prominently featured on the "What's New" section of the ICSI official website, serving as a reminder for all aspiring Company Secretaries.
*   Candidates who wished to appear for the CSEET January 2026 examination had to complete their registration by this date. The examination is scheduled for January 10, 2026.

## Read the Official Document
*   [Visit the Official ICSI Website for CSEET Information](https://www.icsi.edu/cseet/)

*Published on: 16 December 2025*
